'''Ministry of Agriculture and Forests''' (MOAF) is ministry of [[Bhutan]] responsible to ensure sustainable social and economic well-being of the Bhutanese people through adequate access to food and natural resources.<ref>http://www.moaf.gov.bt/aboutus/the-ministry/</ref>
