The '''Ministry of Education''' ({{lang-am|የትምህርት ሚኒሰቴር }}) is a governmental ministry of [[Ethiopia]]. It is headquartered in Arada Sub-City, [[Addis Ababa]].<ref>"[http://www.moe.gov.et/contact-us?p_p_id=82&p_p_lifecycle=1&p_p_state=normal&p_p_mode=view&_82_struts_action=/language/view&_82_redirect=/contact-us&_82_languageId=en_US Contact Us]." Ministry of Education of Ethiopia. Retrieved on 6 June 2018. "Arada Sub-City, Addis Ababa, Ethiopia" - [http://www.moe.gov.et/contact-us?p_p_id=82&p_p_lifecycle=1&p_p_state=normal&p_p_mode=view&_82_struts_action=/language/view&_82_redirect=/contact-us&_82_languageId=am_ET Address in Amharic]: "አዲስ አበባ ፣ አራዳ ክፍለ ከተማ፣"</ref>

